VERSION 1.0.0
------------------------
   o Added T_regularization param to Machima2()
     ("frobenius_unit", "l2") to prevent H_Sym collapse
     when T is a free dense matrix
   o Fixed NA in dimnames of H_Sym/H_RNA when J > num_celltypes
     (falls back to "comp_j")

VERSION 0.99.1
------------------------
   o Added Machima2() for symmetric epigenomic matrices
   o Added init_W_RNA/init_H_RNA/init_H_Sym, fixH_Sym to Machima2()
   o Added nmf_init_n_restart/num_iter/algorithm params
   o Exported Mat2List()
   o Fixed BetaDivergence formula (operator precedence + X/Y swap)
   o Fixed L1_W_RNA unused in W_RNA updates
   o Fixed horizontal mode RecError mismatch
   o Removed dead code in orthogonal H_RNA update
   o Extracted shared .estimateCelltypes()

VERSION 0.99.0
------------------------
   o Package released
